愿双眼所及 的视线 带梦想穿越 境界线
yuàn shuāngyǎn suǒ jí de shìxiàn dài mèngxiǎng chuānyuè jìngjiè xiàn
棱镜千万面 绚烂 千万遍 因一个焦点 而繁衍
léngjìng qiān wàn miàn xuànlàn qiān wàn biàn yīn yīgè jiāodiǎn ér fányǎn
愿双眼所及 的视线 带梦想跨越 地平线
yuàn shuāngyǎn suǒ jí de shìxiàn dài mèngxiǎng kuàyuè dìpíngxiàn
连接每一个 终点 的光线 因为你 而成为梦想的 起源
liánjiē měi yīgè zhōngdiǎn de guāngxiàn yīnwèi nǐ ér chéngwéi mèngxiǎng de qǐyuán

看见了丛林城堡 有人与魔法结缘
kànjiànle cónglín chéngbǎo yǒurén yǔ mófǎ jiéyuán
看见了水墨画卷 有人在吟唱诗篇
kànjiànle shuǐmòhuà juàn yǒurén zài yínchàng shīpiān
看见了有些星光 虽微小却很耀眼 有些梦 虽遥远 总会实现
kànjiànle yǒuxiē xīngguāng suī wéixiǎo què hěn yàoyǎn yǒuxiē mèng suī yáoyuǎn zǒng huì shíxiàn
看见了晨曦初现 又是动人的明天
kànjiànle chénxī chū xiàn yòu shì dòngrén de míngtiān
看见了自我渺小 才懂得 宇宙的宏愿
kànjiànle zìwǒ miǎoxiǎo cái dǒngdé yǔzhòu de hóngyuàn

坚定双眼 别 移开视线
jiāndìng shuāngyǎn bié yí kāi shìxiàn

愿双眼所及 的视线 带梦想穿越 境界线
yuàn shuāngyǎn suǒ jí de shìxiàn dài mèngxiǎng chuānyuè jìngjiè xiàn
棱镜千万面 绚烂 千万遍 因一个焦点 而繁衍
léngjìng qiān wàn miàn xuànlàn qiān wàn biàn yīn yīgè jiāodiǎn ér fányǎn

愿双眼所及 的视线 带梦想跨越 地平线
yuàn shuāngyǎn suǒ jí de shìxiàn dài mèngxiǎng kuàyuè dìpíngxiàn
连接每一个 终点 的光线 因为你……
liánjiē měi yīgè zhōngdiǎn de guāngxiàn yīnwèi nǐ……

你充满渴望 的信念 让我们成为 你双眼
nǐ chōngmǎn kěwàng de xìnniàn ràng wǒmen chéngwéi nǐ shuāngyǎn
万花筒表演 绚烂 千万遍 因你是焦点 而繁衍
wànhuātǒng biǎoyǎn xuànlàn qiān wàn biàn yīn nǐ shì jiāodiǎn ér fányǎn
眺望向天空 的视线 带梦想跨越 地平线
tiàowàng xiàng tiānkōng de shìxiàn dài mèngxiǎng kuàyuè dìpíngxiàn
连接每一个 终点 的光线 因为你 聚焦成一点……
liánjiē měi yīgè zhōngdiǎn de guāngxiàn yīnwèi nǐ jùjiāo chéng yīdiǎn……

Translation:
I look forward to being gently awakened by you every tomorrow
To open up new world with full vitality in ignorance
I hope tomorrow will not be covered by dark clouds as you expect
Stupid and determined to travel 30000 miles to discover new scenery

Give us (life) to focus on the flight against the light
Waving wings (moving forward), walking (non-stop) and looking up at your back

May the vision within your eyes lead your dreams across the border
Prisms with thousands of gorgeous faces multiply with one focus
May the vision within your eyes lead your dream across the horizon
The light connecting each end comes because of you

Even if tomorrow's aimless destination is forgotten
Confused, maybe without a destination, I find myself
So it will be easy to smile when you are full of energy tomorrow
Open your eyes and travel 30 thousand miles with determination to discover new meaning

Give us (life) to focus on the flight against the light
Waving wings (moving forward), walking (non-stop) and looking up at your back

May the vision within your eyes lead your dreams across the border
Prisms with thousands of gorgeous faces multiply with one focus
May the vision within your eyes lead your dream across the horizon
The light connecting each destination becomes the origin of dreams because of you

I Saw someone in the jungle castle who became attached to magic
I saw the ink painting. Someone was singing poems
I saw some small but dazzling stars. Some dreams will come true even though they are far away
Seeing the dawn is a moving tomorrow
Only when you see yourself small can you understand the grand wish of the universe

Keep your eyes fixed and don't look away
May the vision within your eyes lead your dreams across the border
Prisms with thousands of gorgeous faces multiply with one focus
May the vision within your eyes lead your dream across the horizon
The light that connects every destination because of you

Your faith full of desire makes us your eyes
The kaleidoscope performs brilliantly and thrives because you are the focus
Overlooking the sky, taking dreams across the horizon
Connect the light at each end because you focus on one point
